(Sorry, I didn't mean to, I appologize)

::Spears::
She looked at Lunarpine. "I..ah.don't know."  Her body shook slightly 
as the trainer program took over. "If you think that I really need to 
go, then I will go where I am needed."  

Her trainer side wanted to gather as much info about the maximals as 
possable and then give it to Prebon.  

She walked up to Lunarpine.  "Yes, I'll go with you." She lowered her 
head and followed Lunarpine, pretending to be timid and shy. Her 
trainer mind sceeming with every step she took.
